OL,3,CGirl, 12, suffers life-threatening
OL,4,Cinjuries in three-car crash
OL,6,FBoth children were passengers in an
OL,7,FAudi car involved in the crash. The
OL,8,Ffemale driver of that car and another
OL,9,Fpassenger are also in hospital with
OL,10,Flife-changing injuries.
OL,12,FThe other two vehicles involved in the
OL,13,Fincident were a silver Mercedes A200
OL,14,Fand a silver BMW 118.
OL,16,FThe male driver of the Mercedes
OL,17,Fremains at Ysbyty Glan Clwyd with
OL,18,Fserious, life-changing injuries.
