OL,3,CGirl, 12, suffers life-threatening
OL,4,Cinjuries in three-car crash
OL,6,FTwo men were arrested following the
OL,7,Fcrash - the male passenger of the
OL,8,FMercedes and the 20-year-old driver of
OL,9,Fthe BMW.
OL,11,FThe BMW driver was initially taken to
OL,12,Fhospital with slight injuries and was
OL,13,Flater arrested on suspicion of causing
OL,14,Fserious injuries by dangerous driving.
OL,15,FHe has since been released under
OL,16,Finvestigation.
OL,18,FThe male passenger of the Mercedes,
OL,19,Fwho was also arrested, was later taken
OL,20,Fto Ysbyty Glan Clwyd where he remains
OL,21,Fwith serious injuries.
