OL,3,CGirl, 12, suffers life-threatening
OL,4,Cinjuries in three-car crash
OL,6,FPolice have renewed their appeal for
OL,7,Fwitnesses and dash cam footage
OL,8,Ffollowing the collision.
OL,10,FDetective Sergeant Katie Davies of the
OL,11,FSerious Collision Investigation Unit
OL,12,Fsaid: "Our thoughts remain with all
OL,13,Fwho are in hospital, and I would like
OL,14,Fto stress that the investigation to
OL,15,Ffind out what happened is now underway.
OL,17,F"We'd like to thank all those who have
OL,18,Falready contacted us, however we
OL,19,Fcontinue to urge anybody who may have
OL,20,Finformation that could assist with our
OL,21,Finvestigation to come forward.
