OL,6,F"This includes anybody who may have
OL,7,Fbeen travelling in the area and who
OL,8,Fmay have dash cam footage showing the
OL,9,Fsilver BMW 118 and Silver Mercedes
OL,10,Fbeing driven prior to the collision.
OL,12,F"I would like to thank the local
OL,13,Fcommunity and motorists for their
OL,14,Fpatience whilst the road was closed to
OL,15,Fallow our officers and staff to carry
OL,16,Fout their initial enquiries.
